headline: Eaton (ETN) Earnings Expected to Grow: What to Know Ahead of Next Week's Release

headline: A.O. Smith (AOS) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: A.O. Smith (AOS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +5.62% and +0.69%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
